Over the years MIC institute has developed as centre of excellence in the filed of computer education and offering various govt. recognized courses and other allied services related to computers. MIC as a non profit making organization run by MIC Education and Social Welfare Society and is dedicated to the service of the society. MIC has an association with Makhanlal Chaturvedi Rashtriya Patrakarita Vishvavidyalaya, Bhopal (M.P.) for its Master Degree Courses, Bachelor Degree, Post Graduate Diploma and Diploma courses, 1 year Post Graduate Diploma in Computer Application(PGDCA), and 1 year Diploma Computer Application (DCA). Student's result itself narrates the story of the MIC glorious success.Our Mission statement is to provide a quality product/service that exceeds the expectations of our students, no exceptions. Our well experienced/certified trainers lead the students through the classes without the use of in class manuals. We use the manual as a post-training tool, not as a training substitute! For many of our classes we also provide students with our exclusive cheat sheets. These are MIC trainer developed reference guides that outline the tricks and tools learned during the class. All of MIC classes are 100% guaranteed and, as usual at MIC, all of our students receive post-training telephone support at no charge . . . forever.

Details: NIIT Ltd. is a leading Global Talent Development Corporation, building skilled manpower pool for global industry requirements. The company which was set up in 1981, to help the nascent IT industry overcome its human resource challenges, has today grown to be amongst worlds leading talent development companies offering learning solutions to Individuals, Enterprises and Institutions across 40 countries. Leading IT journal Dataquest has conferred upon NIIT the Top IT Training Company award successively for the past 20 years, since the inception of this category. NIIT Ltd. training solutions in IT, Banking, Finance and Insurance, Knowledge Process Outsourcing (KPO), Business Process Management (BPM), Executive Management Education, Vocational Skills, School Learning Solutions and Communication and Professional Life Skills has impacted over 35 million learners since inception. NIIT Ltd. expertise in learning content development, training delivery and education process management make it the most preferred training partner, worldwide. NIIT Ltd. has been ranked 4th in Best companies to work for in India, 2013-14, by Great Place to Work Institute and Top 10 Best Employers in India- 2011 by Aon Hewitt. The company has also been voted the second most trusted education brand in India by Brand Equity- Nielsen Survey 2011. Contact us for further details.

Details: An ISO 9001 Certified & Govt. Registered Institute. We are providing quality concept based computer education at reasonable rates for the last 14+ years by well experianced MCA Faculty. Institute is run by Professionals, for Professionals. MIC Computer Education, Bhopal focuses on concept based training instead of cramming using latest art of technology i.e. Multimedia LCD Projector.MISSION INFORMATION COMMUNICATION, Bhopal or MIC, Bhopal is the prestigious and pioneer academy of Madhya Pradesh was established in the year 2000 with the objective of providing Quality education and services in the field of Career Oriented Courses, The institute develops education quality in the field of computer technology its training and development courses. Over the years MIC institute has developed as centre of excellence in the filed of computer education and offering various govt. recognized courses and other allied services related to computers. MIC as a non profit making organization run by MIC Education and Social Welfare Society and is dedicated to the service of the society. MIC has an association with Makhanlal Chaturvedi Rashtriya Patrakarita Vishvavidyalaya, Bhopal (M.P.) for its Master Degree Courses, Bachelor Degree, Post Graduate Diploma and Diploma courses, 1 year Post Graduate Diploma in Computer Application(PGDCA), and 1 year Diploma Computer Application (DCA). For a number of years MIC Students are the toppers in the Makhanlal University examinations. Student's result itself narrates the story of the MIC glorious success.Our Mission statement is to provide a quality product/service that exceeds the expectations of our students, no exceptions. We teach a range of classes that start with the very basic computer user and extends to the very advanced MCITP student. We are teaching .NET, PHP, Web Designing, .NET projects, VB.NET, ASP.NET, C#.NET, Flash, Website Creation, Live Projects, Dreamweaver, Tally, CSS coaching, 6 months, 6 weeks training of all Types of Trainings, BCA, MCA Final Year Projects are done in our centre for the last 14+ yrs. At MIC, each student learns using their own state of the art computer with no more than 12 students in a class. Our well experienced/certified trainers lead the students through the classes without the use of in class manuals. We use the manual as a post-training tool, not as a training substitute! For many of our classes we also provide students with our exclusive cheat sheets. These are MIC trainer developed reference guides that outline the tricks and tools learned during the class. All of MIC classes are 100% guaranteed and, as usual at MIC, all of our students receive post-training telephone support at no charge . . . forever.

Details: An ISO 9001 Certified & Govt. Registered Institute. We are providing quality concept based computer education at reasonable rates for the last 14+ years by well experianced MCA Faculty. Institute is run by Professionals, for Professionals. MIC Computer Education, Bhopal focuses on concept based training instead of cramming using latest art of technology i.e. Multimedia LCD Projector.MISSION INFORMATION COMMUNICATION, Bhopal or MIC, Bhopal is the prestigious and pioneer academy of Madhya Pradesh was established in the year 2000 with the objective of providing Quality education and services in the field of Career Oriented Courses, The institute develops education quality in the field of computer technology its training and development courses. Over the years MIC institute has developed as centre of excellence in the filed of computer education and offering various govt. recognized courses and other allied services related to computers. MIC as a non profit making organization run by MIC Education and Social Welfare Society and is dedicated to the service of the society. MIC has an association with Makhanlal Chaturvedi Rashtriya Patrakarita Vishvavidyalaya, Bhopal (M.P.) for its Master Degree Courses, Bachelor Degree, Post Graduate Diploma and Diploma courses, 1 year Post Graduate Diploma in Computer Application(PGDCA), and 1 year Diploma Computer Application (DCA). For a number of years MIC Students are the toppers in the Makhanlal University examinations. Student's result itself narrates the story of the MIC glorious success.Our Mission statement is to provide a quality product/service that exceeds the expectations of our students, no exceptions. We teach a range of classes that start with the very basic computer user and extends to the very advanced MCITP student. We are teaching .NET, PHP, Web Designing, .NET projects, VB.NET, ASP.NET, C#.NET, Flash, Website Creation, Live Projects, Dreamweaver, Tally, CSS coaching, 6 months, 6 weeks training of all Types of Trainings, BCA, MCA Final Year Projects are done in our centre for the last 14+ yrs. At MIC, each student learns using their own state of the art computer with no more than 12 students in a class. Our well experienced/certified trainers lead the students through the classes without the use of in class manuals. We use the manual as a post-training tool, not as a training substitute! For many of our classes we also provide students with our exclusive cheat sheets. These are MIC trainer developed reference guides that outline the tricks and tools learned during the class. All of MIC classes are 100% guaranteed and, as usual at MIC, all of our students receive post-training telephone support at no charge . . . forever.

Details: An ISO 9001 Certified & Govt. Registered Institute. We are providing quality concept based computer education at reasonable rates for the last 14+ years by well experianced MCA Faculty. Institute is run by Professionals, for Professionals. MIC Computer Education, Bhopal focuses on concept based training instead of cramming using latest art of technology i.e. Multimedia LCD Projector.MISSION INFORMATION COMMUNICATION, Bhopal or MIC, Bhopal is the prestigious and pioneer academy of Madhya Pradesh was established in the year 2000 with the objective of providing Quality education and services in the field of Career Oriented Courses, The institute develops education quality in the field of computer technology its training and development courses. Over the years MIC institute has developed as centre of excellence in the filed of computer education and offering various govt. recognized courses and other allied services related to computers. MIC as a non profit making organization run by MIC Education and Social Welfare Society and is dedicated to the service of the society. MIC has an association with Makhanlal Chaturvedi Rashtriya Patrakarita Vishvavidyalaya, Bhopal (M.P.) for its Master Degree Courses, Bachelor Degree, Post Graduate Diploma and Diploma courses, 1 year Post Graduate Diploma in Computer Application(PGDCA), and 1 year Diploma Computer Application (DCA). For a number of years MIC Students are the toppers in the Makhanlal University examinations. Student's result itself narrates the story of the MIC glorious success.Our Mission statement is to provide a quality product/service that exceeds the expectations of our students, no exceptions. We teach a range of classes that start with the very basic computer user and extends to the very advanced MCITP student. We are teaching .NET, PHP, Web Designing, .NET projects, VB.NET, ASP.NET, C#.NET, Flash, Website Creation, Live Projects, Dreamweaver, Tally, CSS coaching, 6 months, 6 weeks training of all Types of Trainings, BCA, MCA Final Year Projects are done in our centre for the last 14+ yrs. At MIC, each student learns using their own state of the art computer with no more than 12 students in a class. Our well experienced/certified trainers lead the students through the classes without the use of in class manuals. We use the manual as a post-training tool, not as a training substitute! For many of our classes we also provide students with our exclusive cheat sheets. These are MIC trainer developed reference guides that outline the tricks and tools learned during the class. All of MIC classes are 100% guaranteed and, as usual at MIC, all of our students receive post-training telephone support at no charge . . . forever.

Student's result itself narrates the story of the MIC glorious success.Our Mission statement is to provide a quality product/service that exceeds the expectations of our students, no exceptions. in the City of Lake - BHOPAL and the Heart of India,(M.P.)Founder : Piyush Shukla (Director).
ISE Special thank to Base Supporting Members Suman Datta, Sudeep Rathore, Neeraj Shukla, Abhay Pathak, Prashant PillaiISE is a Premier Provider of Professional IT Training and Business solutions.ISE is a promising name, is involved in Computer Literacy Programs, Minor / Major Training, e-Business Solution, Software Development, Web Designing & its Marketing, SEO, Presentation Designing,EDP, IT-Consultancy & Job Consultancy.For the last few years there has been immense change in the field of Information Technology. The IT industry is already famous for Fast changes. To cope-up with this fast advancing technology ISE has taken the challenge and has equipped itself for providing Professional Training with most Modern Technology and Techniques. The ambience of the institute is designed to be in perfect coherence with the nature of functions besides being very inspiring for students to gain practical industrial knowledge.ISE is one of the fast growing institutes with diverse range of courses including the ones for which one never had an option except moving to metro cities which is an expensive affair. The courses are given job oriented professional touch enabling them to solve problems on the spot.Well equipped library, lab, training rooms, development & designing cell and highly sophisticated ambience and very highly qualified staff of software and network engineers, architects, analysts, programmers, developers, designers and administrators who provide valuable training and make an impact to their customers & trainees maintain excellent standards makes it a perfect place for Professional Training & Development.ISE is very proud of the people that work for them. ISE has a hardworking staff of very high-integrity individuals that focus on doing the best for Trainees and the Customer everyday. ISE has a highly trained staff that makes an impact to their customers everyday. Each employee of ISE is focused on construct strong business results.

Details: NIIT Ltd. is a leading Global Talent Development Corporation, building skilled manpower pool for global industry requirements. The company which was set up in 1981, to help the nascent IT industry overcome its human resource challenges, has today grown to be amongst worlds leading talent development companies offering learning solutions to Individuals, Enterprises and Institutions across 40 countries. Leading IT journal Dataquest has conferred upon NIIT the Top IT Training Company award successively for the past 20 years, since the inception of this category. NIIT Ltd. training solutions in IT, Banking, Finance and Insurance, Knowledge Process Outsourcing (KPO), Business Process Management (BPM), Executive Management Education, Vocational Skills, School Learning Solutions and Communication and Professional Life Skills has impacted over 35 million learners since inception. NIIT Ltd. expertise in learning content development, training delivery and education process management make it the most preferred training partner, worldwide. NIIT Ltd. has been ranked 4th in Best companies to work for in India, 2013-14, by Great Place to Work Institute and Top 10 Best Employers in India- 2011 by Aon Hewitt. The company has also been voted the second most trusted education brand in India by Brand Equity- Nielsen Survey 2011. Contact us for further details.

Details: An ISO 9001 Certified & Govt. Registered Institute. We are providing quality concept based computer education at reasonable rates for the last 14+ years by well experianced MCA Faculty. Institute is run by Professionals, for Professionals. MIC Computer Education, Bhopal focuses on concept based training instead of cramming using latest art of technology i.e. Multimedia LCD Projector.MISSION INFORMATION COMMUNICATION, Bhopal or MIC, Bhopal is the prestigious and pioneer academy of Madhya Pradesh was established in the year 2000 with the objective of providing Quality education and services in the field of Career Oriented Courses, The institute develops education quality in the field of computer technology its training and development courses. Over the years MIC institute has developed as centre of excellence in the filed of computer education and offering various govt. recognized courses and other allied services related to computers. MIC as a non profit making organization run by MIC Education and Social Welfare Society and is dedicated to the service of the society. MIC has an association with Makhanlal Chaturvedi Rashtriya Patrakarita Vishvavidyalaya, Bhopal (M.P.) for its Master Degree Courses, Bachelor Degree, Post Graduate Diploma and Diploma courses, 1 year Post Graduate Diploma in Computer Application(PGDCA), and 1 year Diploma Computer Application (DCA). For a number of years MIC Students are the toppers in the Makhanlal University examinations. Student's result itself narrates the story of the MIC glorious success.Our Mission statement is to provide a quality product/service that exceeds the expectations of our students, no exceptions. We teach a range of classes that start with the very basic computer user and extends to the very advanced MCITP student. We are teaching .NET, PHP, Web Designing, .NET projects, VB.NET, ASP.NET, C#.NET, Flash, Website Creation, Live Projects, Dreamweaver, Tally, CSS coaching, 6 months, 6 weeks training of all Types of Trainings, BCA, MCA Final Year Projects are done in our centre for the last 14+ yrs. At MIC, each student learns using their own state of the art computer with no more than 12 students in a class. Our well experienced/certified trainers lead the students through the classes without the use of in class manuals. We use the manual as a post-training tool, not as a training substitute! For many of our classes we also provide students with our exclusive cheat sheets. These are MIC trainer developed reference guides that outline the tricks and tools learned during the class. All of MIC classes are 100% guaranteed and, as usual at MIC, all of our students receive post-training telephone support at no charge . . . forever.

The IT industry is already famous for Fast changes. To cope-up with this fast advancing technology ISE has taken the challenge and has equipped itself for providing Professional Training with most Modern Technology and Techniques. The ambience of the institute is designed to be in perfect coherence with the nature of functions besides being very inspiring for students to gain practical industrial knowledge.ISE is one of the fast growing institutes with diverse range of courses including the ones for which one never had an option except moving to metro cities which is an expensive affair. The courses are given job oriented professional touch enabling them to solve problems on the spot.Well equipped library, lab, training rooms, development & designing cell and highly sophisticated ambience and very highly qualified staff of software and network engineers, architects, analysts, programmers, developers, designers and administrators who provide valuable training and make an impact to their customers & trainees maintain excellent standards makes it a perfect place for Professional Training & Development.ISE is very proud of the people that work for them. ISE has a hardworking staff of very high-integrity individuals that focus on doing the best for Trainees and the Customer everyday. ISE has a highly trained staff that makes an impact to their customers everyday. Each employee of ISE is focused on construct strong business results.

Details: NIIT Ltd. is a leading Global Talent Development Corporation, building skilled manpower pool for global industry requirements. The company which was set up in 1981, to help the nascent IT industry overcome its human resource challenges, has today grown to be amongst worlds leading talent development companies offering learning solutions to Individuals, Enterprises and Institutions across 40 countries. Leading IT journal Dataquest has conferred upon NIIT the Top IT Training Company award successively for the past 20 years, since the inception of this category. NIIT Ltd. training solutions in IT, Banking, Finance and Insurance, Knowledge Process Outsourcing (KPO), Business Process Management (BPM), Executive Management Education, Vocational Skills, School Learning Solutions and Communication and Professional Life Skills has impacted over 35 million learners since inception. NIIT Ltd. expertise in learning content development, training delivery and education process management make it the most preferred training partner, worldwide. NIIT Ltd. has been ranked 4th in Best companies to work for in India, 2013-14, by Great Place to Work Institute and Top 10 Best Employers in India- 2011 by Aon Hewitt. The company has also been voted the second most trusted education brand in India by Brand Equity- Nielsen Survey 2011. Contact us for further details.

Details: An ISO 9001 Certified & Govt. Registered Institute. We are providing quality concept based computer education at reasonable rates for the last 14+ years by well experianced MCA Faculty. Institute is run by Professionals, for Professionals. MIC Computer Education, Bhopal focuses on concept based training instead of cramming using latest art of technology i.e. Multimedia LCD Projector.MISSION INFORMATION COMMUNICATION, Bhopal or MIC, Bhopal is the prestigious and pioneer academy of Madhya Pradesh was established in the year 2000 with the objective of providing Quality education and services in the field of Career Oriented Courses, The institute develops education quality in the field of computer technology its training and development courses. Over the years MIC institute has developed as centre of excellence in the filed of computer education and offering various govt. recognized courses and other allied services related to computers. MIC as a non profit making organization run by MIC Education and Social Welfare Society and is dedicated to the service of the society. MIC has an association with Makhanlal Chaturvedi Rashtriya Patrakarita Vishvavidyalaya, Bhopal (M.P.) for its Master Degree Courses, Bachelor Degree, Post Graduate Diploma and Diploma courses, 1 year Post Graduate Diploma in Computer Application(PGDCA), and 1 year Diploma Computer Application (DCA). For a number of years MIC Students are the toppers in the Makhanlal University examinations. Student's result itself narrates the story of the MIC glorious success.Our Mission statement is to provide a quality product/service that exceeds the expectations of our students, no exceptions. We teach a range of classes that start with the very basic computer user and extends to the very advanced MCITP student. We are teaching .NET, PHP, Web Designing, .NET projects, VB.NET, ASP.NET, C#.NET, Flash, Website Creation, Live Projects, Dreamweaver, Tally, CSS coaching, 6 months, 6 weeks training of all Types of Trainings, BCA, MCA Final Year Projects are done in our centre for the last 14+ yrs. At MIC, each student learns using their own state of the art computer with no more than 12 students in a class. Our well experienced/certified trainers lead the students through the classes without the use of in class manuals. We use the manual as a post-training tool, not as a training substitute! For many of our classes we also provide students with our exclusive cheat sheets. These are MIC trainer developed reference guides that outline the tricks and tools learned during the class. All of MIC classes are 100% guaranteed and, as usual at MIC, all of our students receive post-training telephone support at no charge . . . forever.
